<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fils de Projet — Maintenance Web</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --surface: #111111;
    --surface-2: #161616;
    --surface-3: #1c1c1c;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --border-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    --text: #e8e8e8;
    --text-muted: #6b6b6b;
    --text-dim: #4a4a4a;
    --green: #00c853;
    --green-dim: rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.08);
    --green-border: rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.2);
    --white: #ffffff;
    --radius: 8px;
    --radius-sm: 5px;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 32px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1.15; }
  .nav-logo .logo-line { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; align-items: baseline; }
  .nav-logo .initial { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(0,200,83,0.9), 0 0 16px rgba(0,200,83,0.45); letter-spacing: 0; line-height: 1; margin-right: 2px; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 4px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); background: var(--surface-2); }
  .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .btn-nav { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .btn-nav-ghost { background: var(--surface-2); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); }
  .btn-nav-ghost:hover { background: var(--surface-3); }
  .btn-nav-primary { background: var(--green); color: #000; }
  .btn-nav-primary:hover { background: #00e060; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 32px 80px; }
  .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green); background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 32px; }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(38px, 5.5vw, 68px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero-title .hero-intro {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.2vw, 14px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .hero-title .fdp-static {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .hero-title .fdp-scrub-char {
    display: inline-block;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }
  .hero-title .fdp-scrub-char.ellipsis {
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .hero-title .fdp-scrub-char.projet-word {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .hero-title .dim { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; }

  .hero-desc { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--green); color: #000; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #00e060; }
  .btn-secondary { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .hero-meta { display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .hero-meta-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); }
  .hero-meta-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.25; }
  .section-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 40px; }

  /* PAIN GRID */
  .pain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
  .pain-item { background: var(--surface); padding: 24px; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .pain-item:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .pain-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--surface-3); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .pain-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pain-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  /* Quote copy inline dans les pain items */
  .pain-quote { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 8px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-style: italic; }

  /* AUDIT */
  .audit-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .audit-card-header { padding: 20px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .audit-card-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--white); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .tag { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 100px; }
  .tag-green { background: var(--green-dim); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); }
  .tag-grey { background: var(--surface-3); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .audit-card-body { padding: 20px 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .audit-item-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .audit-item-val { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* OUTCOMES WRAPPER avec flèche SVG */
  .outcomes-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 8px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .audit-arrow-svg {
    width: 60px;
    height: 300px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .outcomes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .outcome-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .outcome-card.lit {
    border-color: var(--green-border);
    background: #0d1a12;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--green-border);
  }
  .outcome-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); background: var(--surface-2); }
  .outcome-icon { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .outcome-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .outcome-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .outcomes-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr; }
    .audit-arrow-svg { width: 40px; }
  }

  .price-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 24px; margin-top: 32px; }
  .price-amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); }
  .price-detail { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }
  .price-green { color: var(--green); }

  /* PRICE BLOCK */
  .price-block { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; margin-top: 32px; }
  .price-block-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface-2); }
  .price-block-body { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; padding: 0; }
  .price-tier { flex: 1; padding: 24px; }
  .price-tier-amount { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .price-tier-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .price-tier-detail { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .price-tier:first-child { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .price-tier-sep { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-dim); padding: 0 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .price-block-footer { padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface-2); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* CONDITIONS BLOCK */
  .conditions-block { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px 24px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .conditions-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .conditions-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .conditions-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .conditions-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 7px; }

  /* PLANS */
  .plans-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
  .plan-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; transition: border-color 0.15s; }
  .plan-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); }
  .plan-card.featured { border-color: var(--green-border); background: #0d1a12; }
  .plan-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .plan-card.featured .plan-name { color: var(--green); }
  .plan-price { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .plan-period { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .plan-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .plan-card.featured .plan-divider { background: var(--green-border); }
  .plan-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 28px; flex: 1; }
  .plan-feature { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; line-height: 1.5; }
  .plan-feature-check { color: var(--green); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .plan-ideal { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 8px 12px; background: var(--surface-3); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); line-height: 1.5; }
  .plan-cta { display: block; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; padding: 9px 16px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.15s; cursor: pointer; border: none; }
  .plan-cta-default { background: var(--surface-3); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); }
  .plan-cta-default:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .plan-cta-featured { background: var(--green); color: #000; }
  .plan-cta-featured:hover { background: #00e060; }

  .banner { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 14px 20px; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--green); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TERMINAL */
  .terminal { background: #080808; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; margin-top: 32px; }
  .terminal-header { background: var(--surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 10px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .dot-r { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-y { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot-g { background: #28c840; }
  .terminal-filename { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-left: 10px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
  .terminal-body { padding: 20px 24px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2; }
  .t-line { display: block; }
  .t-prompt { color: var(--green); user-select: none; }
  .t-cmd { color: #e8e8e8; }
  .t-comment { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .t-out { color: #888; }
  .t-success { color: var(--green); }
  .t-warn { color: #f0a500; }
  .t-blink::after { content: '▋'; color: var(--green); animation: blink 1s infinite; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .cta-inner { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 56px 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .cta-inner::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(0,200,83,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
  .cta-title { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cta-sub2 { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 32px; font-style: italic; }
  .cta-hint { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 16px; }

  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 24px 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-logo { display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1.15; }
  .footer-logo .logo-line { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; align-items: baseline; }
  .footer-logo .initial { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(0,200,83,0.9), 0 0 16px rgba(0,200,83,0.45); letter-spacing: 0; line-height: 1; margin-right: 2px; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
  .footer-links span { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .footer-right { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }

  .hero-reveal-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    opacity: 1;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }
  .hero-reveal-hint.hidden { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-reveal-hint::before { content: '↓'; font-size: 10px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--surface-3); border-radius: 3px; }

  @keyframes blink { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0; } }
  @keyframes bounce-hint { 0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(3px); } }
  .hero-reveal-hint::before { animation: bounce-hint 1.5s infinite; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pain-grid, .outcomes-grid, .plans-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .audit-card-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 0 16px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hero, .section, .cta-section { padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; }
    .cta-inner { padding: 32px 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-left">
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <span class="logo-line"><span class="initial">F</span>ils</span>
      <span class="logo-line"><span class="initial">d</span>e</span>
      <span class="logo-line"><span class="initial">P</span>rojet</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#audit">Audit</a></li>
      <li><a href="#plans">Formules</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="#plans" class="btn-nav btn-nav-ghost">Voir les formules</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-nav btn-nav-primary">Prendre RDV</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Freelance indépendant — Maintenance web</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="hero-intro">Quand tu reçois le mail de l'agence qui te fait dire…</span>
    « <span class="fdp-static">Fils de</span><span id="fdp-scrub"></span> »
  </h1>
  <div class="hero-reveal-hint">scroll pour révéler</div>
  <p class="hero-desc">
    C'est exactement là qu'intervient Fils de Projet. Seul aux commandes, direct, sans intermédiaire. Ton site géré sérieusement — WordPress, Shopify, CMS no-code.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Démarrer par un audit →</a>
    <a href="#plans" class="btn-secondary">Voir les formules</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <span class="hero-meta-val">500–900€</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-label">Audit complet</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <span class="hero-meta-val">5–7 j</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-label">Délai de livraison</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <span class="hero-meta-val">0</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-label">Engagement requis</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <span class="hero-meta-val">1</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-label">Interlocuteur</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section" id="why">
  <div class="section-label">Pourquoi Fils de Projet</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Ce que les agences font mal.</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">Tu paies pour un service. Tu obtiens de la bureaucratie.</p>
  <div class="pain-grid">
    <div class="pain-item">
      <div class="pain-icon">⏳</div>
      <div class="pain-title">Les délais</div>
      <div class="pain-desc">3 semaines pour modifier un texte. Quand t'as un interlocuteur disponible.</div>
      <div class="pain-quote">"C'est en cours de traitement."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-item">
      <div class="pain-icon">👻</div>
      <div class="pain-title">Les interlocuteurs fantômes</div>
      <div class="pain-desc">Le chef de projet change tous les 6 mois. Personne ne connaît ton site.</div>
      <div class="pain-quote">"Je reprends le dossier, tu peux me re-expliquer ?"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-item">
      <div class="pain-icon">💸</div>
      <div class="pain-title">L'opacité</div>
      <div class="pain-desc">Tu paies sans savoir ce que ça couvre. Les devis arrivent après les surprises.</div>
      <div class="pain-quote">"Ce n'était pas inclus dans le forfait initial."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-item">
      <div class="pain-icon">🔇</div>
      <div class="pain-title">Le silence radio</div>
      <div class="pain-desc">Ton site plante un dimanche. Tu l'apprends le lundi en ouvrant tes mails.</div>
      <div class="pain-quote">"On a été alerté, on traite ça en priorité."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-item">
      <div class="pain-icon">🗃️</div>
